Release v1.02 on Jan, 11th 2021
---------------------------------------------------------
- Text files (must have .txt extension) containing a list of file names (one-per-line) can now be passed in as arguments to the -input option.


Release v1.01 on Jan, 08th 2021
---------------------------------------------------------
- Directories can now be passed in as arguments to the -input option.


Release v1.00 on Jan, 07th 2021
---------------------------------------------------------
- Initial release.
